rComments: Great prof! Engaging material, perhaps weekly assignments are a bit much but they're not difficult at all and once you get used to it, it starts to become second nature. Otherwise he's really super cool and simple, straightforward, clear.
Very decent, respectful & simple. Encourages student to participate in non threatening way. Very positive. Help you reflect & engaging but sometimes too easy & boring.
Dr. Smith looked good every class and really got us to think about ethics - very good class discussions!
